sequenceDiagram
    participant Plugin as Plugin Command
    participant Converter as scripts/converter.py
    participant Agent as arckit-plugin/agents/arckit-research.md
    participant Output as .codex/prompts/arckit.research.md
    
    Plugin->>Converter: Command references agent via Task tool
    Converter->>Agent: Read agent definition
    Agent-->>Converter: Full agent prompt body
    Converter->>Converter: Strip frontmatter
    Converter->>Converter: Rewrite paths for platform
    Converter->>Output: Inline agent prompt in command
    
    Note over Output: Command now has full research<br/>instructions instead of Task delegation
